# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# 1. 統一換行符號 (Auto normalize line endings to LF)
# 避免 macOS/Windows 協作時的 CRLF 衝突
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
* text=auto eol=lf

# 明確指定常見純文字檔格式
*.js text eol=lf
*.mjs text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.html text eol=lf
*.css text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# 2. 二進位檔案 (Denote binary files)
# 防止 Git 嘗試將圖片視為純文字進行合併
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# 3. 最佳化 GitHub 專案語言統計 (Linguist)
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# 將這些目錄標記為文件，不計入核心代碼的語言統計
docs/** linguist-documentation
site/** linguist-documentation
AGENTS.md linguist-documentation

# 標記為自動生成，不計入統計，且在 GitHub PR 中預設折疊
dist/** linguist-generated
playwright-report/** linguist-generated
coverage/** linguist-generated

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# 4. 最佳化 Diff 視圖
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# 避免 package-lock.json 產生巨大的 Diff 擾亂 Code Review
package-lock.json -diff
